<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Tompo ô, Tsitoha
 Zanaharinay,
 Asan-tànanao re
 Izao rehetra izao.
 Mahagaga indrindra
 Ny fahaizanao
 Entinao mitondra
 Sy miasa ao.

[V2]
 Hianao, Jehovah
 Ao mandrakizay
 Na miovaova
 Izao rehetra izao.
 Mahagaga indrindra
 Ny fitiavanao
 Tsy mba mety miova
 Ny mandao anay.

[V3]
 Ray niandohana
 fony fahizay ;
 Mbola hiafarana
 koa rahatrizay.
 Raiso moramora
 re ny Zanakao.
 Raha tonga ny ora
 hiantsoanao.</lyrics>
<title>Tompo o, Tsitoha FFPM34</title>
<hymn_number>34</hymn_number>
<author>Midlander Song</author>
</song>